                <head>115. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On November 19, Don <persName corresp="#p_PD1">Paarlberg</persName> briefed the
                    Council on Foreign Economic Policy at its 95th meeting on the foreign economic
                    policy issues facing the United States as a result of the deficit in the balance
                    of payments. The minutes of the meeting are printed as <ref target="#d25"
                        >Document 25</ref>.</p>
            </div>
